{"tid":2073562,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[ FORGED IN FIRE : BEAT THE JUDGES 千錘百煉/鍛刀大賽 : 終於可以挑評判機 ]","createTime":"2020-06-21T12:09:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-21T12:59:52.000Z","uid":69994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1c691a7bc44ab7b4d70587dd6ebc577f027c30dc","tid":2073562,"uid":69994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T12:09:27.000Z","msg":"無印由 2015年 第1季 去到 第7季 第31集 暫時告一段落 S07 E31 ( 06-May-2020 ) .<br />\n<br />\n外傳 BEAT THE JUDGES 於 03-Jun-2020 開始 , 評判下海 ! 歷集冠軍回來挑機 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ! <br />\n每集有 3 位前任冠軍回來參賽 , 曾兩輪撕殺後 , 剩下 1 位參賽者對決 1 位評判 ( 不包括 Doug Marcaida ) , 8 小時內完成作品 .<br />\n依然係 1 萬美元獎金 , 不過如果係評判贏 , 評判要捐曬慈善 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> .<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p9iLKoL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp9iLKoL.png&h=b0bb5075&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">S01 E01 ( 03-Jun-2020 ) Short Sword Damascus</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n第 1 集我暫時搵唔到 , 根據之後兩集 , 第 1 集應該對決 Ben Abbott<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">S01 E02 ( 10-Jun-2020 ) Medieval Times</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n參賽者 : Mark Knapp , Josh Navarrete , Steven Bryan<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VCTf6E3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVCTf6E3.png&h=8a1b1c29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n對決評判 David Baker<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MskREZ8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMskREZ8.png&h=698bc801&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">S01 E03 ( 17-Jun-2020 ) Duel Swords</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n參賽者 : Burt Foster , Jeff Wagenaar , John McNerney<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Bps1hRg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBps1hRg.png&h=cc8ab010&s={SIZ